						<div class="postbody">PHY and PHX don't exist.<br /><br />PHY = TYA PHA<br />PHX = TXA PHA<br /><br />If you need to preserve A, first store A to a temporary variable...<br /><br />STA temp<br />TYA<br />PHA<br />LDA temp</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://nesdoug.com" class="postlink">nesdoug.com</a> -- blog/tutorial on programming for the NES</div>
